--- !u!114 &11400000
MonoBehaviour:
  m_ObjectHideFlags: 0
  m_CorrespondingSourceObject: {fileID: 0}
  m_PrefabInstance: {fileID: 0}
  m_PrefabAsset: {fileID: 0}
  m_GameObject: {fileID: 0}
  m_Enabled: 1
  m_EditorHideFlags: 0
  m_Script: {fileID: 11500000, guid: d6fced335fe0e624e8c9d175d9ff6239, type: 3}
  m_Name: Blacksmith_Dialogue
  m_EditorClassIdentifier: Assembly-CSharp::DialogueData
  startNodeIndex: 0
  nodes:
  - editorLabel: Garrett - Greeting
    lines:
    - speaker: Garrett
      text: Huh. A stranger. My wife mentioned she saw someone come down the mountain
        staircase.
      portraitOverride: {fileID: 0}
      emote: 
      sfx: {fileID: 0}
      sfxVolume: 1
      autoAdvanceDelay: 0
      tags: []
    - speaker: Garrett
      text: "I'm Garrett. I keep the village armed and armored. Or I try to \u2014
        hard to do much when those idiots on the eastern road won't let supply carts
        through."
      portraitOverride: {fileID: 0}
      emote: 
      sfx: {fileID: 0}
      sfxVolume: 1
      autoAdvanceDelay: 0
      tags: []
    - speaker: Garrett
      text: What do you need?
      portraitOverride: {fileID: 0}
      emote: 
      sfx: {fileID: 0}
      sfxVolume: 1
      autoAdvanceDelay: 0
      tags: []
    choices:
    - choiceText: (Any advice for the forest?)
      nextNodeIndex: 1
    - choiceText: (What's the deal with the blocked road?)
      nextNodeIndex: 2
    - choiceText: (Just looking around.)
      nextNodeIndex: 3
    nextNodeIndex: -1
  - editorLabel: Garrett - Forest Advice
    lines:
    - speaker: Garrett
      text: The forest? Keep your weapon drawn. The creatures are weak individually
        but they swarm.
      portraitOverride: {fileID: 0}
      emote: 
      sfx: {fileID: 0}
      sfxVolume: 1
      autoAdvanceDelay: 0
      tags: []
    - speaker: Garrett
      text: If you see one coming, swing first. Get the initiative and you control
        the fight from the start.
      portraitOverride: {fileID: 0}
      emote: 
      sfx: {fileID: 0}
      sfxVolume: 1
      autoAdvanceDelay: 0
      tags: []
    - speaker: Garrett
      text: But if one of them gets the jump on you, you'll be fighting on their
        terms. Momentum matters.
      portraitOverride: {fileID: 0}
      emote: 
      sfx: {fileID: 0}
      sfxVolume: 1
      autoAdvanceDelay: 0
      tags: []
    - speaker: Garrett
      text: "Whatever's causing this, it started deep in the forest somewhere. The
        main clearing is mostly safe \u2014 it's further south where things go bad."
      portraitOverride: {fileID: 0}
      emote: 
      sfx: {fileID: 0}
      sfxVolume: 1
      autoAdvanceDelay: 0
      tags: []
    choices: []
    nextNodeIndex: -1
  - editorLabel: Garrett - Road Rant
    lines:
    - speaker: Garrett
      text: Don't get me started on that road.
      portraitOverride: {fileID: 0}
      emote: 
      sfx: {fileID: 0}
      sfxVolume: 1
      autoAdvanceDelay: 0
      tags: []
    - speaker: Garrett
      text: It's the only connection this village has to the kingdom. Merchants,
        supplies, everything comes through there.
      portraitOverride: {fileID: 0}
      emote: 
      sfx: {fileID: 0}
      sfxVolume: 1
      autoAdvanceDelay: 0
      tags: []
    - speaker: Garrett
      text: Two guards have been blocking it for a week. 'Dangerous creature in the
        region.' But they don't even know what it is or where it is.
      portraitOverride: {fileID: 0}
      emote: 
      sfx: {fileID: 0}
      sfxVolume: 1
      autoAdvanceDelay: 0
      tags: []
    - speaker: Garrett
      text: My wife is stretching our food stores thin. We can't hold out much longer
        like this.
      portraitOverride: {fileID: 0}
      emote: 
      sfx: {fileID: 0}
      sfxVolume: 1
      autoAdvanceDelay: 0
      tags: []
    choices: []
    nextNodeIndex: -1
  - editorLabel: Garrett - Browse
    lines:
    - speaker: Garrett
      text: Look around if you want, but stock's thin.
      portraitOverride: {fileID: 0}
      emote: 
      sfx: {fileID: 0}
      sfxVolume: 1
      autoAdvanceDelay: 0
      tags: []
    - speaker: Garrett
      text: Can't get materials with the road blocked. At this rate I'll be turning
        plowshares into swords.
      portraitOverride: {fileID: 0}
      emote: 
      sfx: {fileID: 0}
      sfxVolume: 1
      autoAdvanceDelay: 0
      tags: []
    choices: []
    nextNodeIndex: -1
